## 📚 Concepts Covered

### 6 Types of Performance Testing

| Type | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| 🔵 Load Testing | Normal and peak load simulation |
| 🔴 Stress Testing | Push beyond normal load to find limits |
| ⚡ Spike Testing | Sudden surge in users |
| ⏳ Endurance Testing | Extended period to detect memory leaks |
| 📈 Scalability Testing | Gradually increasing users |
| 🗄️ Volume Testing | Large data sets |

### Key Performance Metrics

| Metric | What It Measures |
|--------|-----------------|
| Response Time | Time from request to reply (ms) |
| Throughput | Requests handled per second |
| Error Rate | % of failed requests |
| CPU Usage | Server processing power consumed |
| Memory Usage | RAM consumption over time |
| Network Bandwidth | Data flowing per second |

