## 🧪 Test Scenarios

### Scenario 1 — Web Application Load Test

```
Endpoint : https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts
Users    : 50
Ramp-up  : 10 seconds
Loops    : 3
Total    : 150 requests
```

| Metric | Result |
|--------|--------|
| Avg Response Time | 75ms ✅ |
| Error Rate | 0.00% ✅ |
| Throughput | 15.0/sec ✅ |

---

### Scenario 2 — API Load Test

```
Endpoint : https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users
Users    : 20
Ramp-up  : 10 seconds
Loops    : 5
Total    : 100 requests
```

| Metric | Result |
|--------|--------|
| Avg Response Time | 66ms ✅ |
| Error Rate | 0.00% ✅ |
| Throughput | 10.3/sec ✅ |

---

### Scenario 3 — Database Load Test

```
Endpoint : https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts/1/comments
Users    : 30
Ramp-up  : 15 seconds
Loops    : 4
Total    : 120 requests
```

| Metric | Result |
|--------|--------|
| Avg Response Time | 262ms ✅ |
| Max Response Time | 8507ms ⚠️ |
| Error Rate | 0.00% ✅ |

> ⚠️ Max response time of 8.5s indicates occasional slow queries under load

---

### Scenario 4 — Gradually Increase Load

```
Endpoint : https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts
Users    : 100
Ramp-up  : 100 seconds (1 user/second)
Loops    : 2
Total    : 200 requests
```

**Finding:**
- Under 20 users → ✅ 200 OK
- Above 20 users → ❌ 429 Too Many Requests

> ⚠️ Breaking point discovered at ~20 concurrent users!

---

### Scenario 5 — Breaking Point Test

```
Endpoint : https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts
Users    : 20
Ramp-up  : 5 seconds
Loops    : 3
Total    : 60 requests
```

| Metric | Result |
|--------|--------|
| Avg Response Time | 71ms ✅ |
| Error Rate | 0.00% ✅ |
| Throughput | 46.0/min ✅ |

> ✅ 20 users = safe limit for this API

