## 🔑 Key Findings

> **Breaking Point:** The JSONPlaceholder API returns `429 Too Many Requests` beyond **20 concurrent users** due to rate limiting.

### Response Codes Encountered

| Code | Meaning | Count |
|------|---------|-------|
| 200 | Success | Most requests |
| 429 | Too Many Requests | Scenario 4 (20+ users) |

